            "answer_text": "Mg3N2 + 6H2O(l) = 3Mg(OH)2 + 2NH3(g) delta G (20C) = -712.9kJ (negative, so the reaction runs) delta H (20C) = -691.2kJ (negative, so the reaction is exothermic) ",
